data.description: Priced to SELL quickly! This 2 BR, 2FB, 2HB townhouse is in great shape! It has a detached garage, fenced rear yard, open kitchen layout and more. 2 large bedrooms on the upper level, each have their own attached full bathroom. GREAT for a rental or roommate situation! Kitchen includes granite counters and large island, stainless steel appliances, upgraded flooring and gas range. The entry level has plenty of space for a future bedroom as needed, a separe living space and half bathroom. Parking is a breeze with dedicated space for each unit via the garage and additional spots, as well as for guest parking in front of the unit. Stonehaven is conveniently located with easy access to schools, restaurants, employment and affordable living for commuters to DC and surrounding military installations. HOA dues are $800/ year and include trash removal, access to seasonal pool and clubhouse, snow removal and community space maintenance.
